                      The membership program offers owners yearly ownership of their dream vehicle. With low monthly
                      automatic payments scheduled over the lif of the agreement from 1 to 99 years.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                      <h5>Subscription</h5>
                      The subscription program offers owners month to month or yearly ownership of their dream vehicle.
                      Automatic payments are scheduled on a month to month or yearly over the life of the agreement up to 8 years.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                      <h5>Fractional</h5>
                      The fractional program offers owners "as-needed":day-to-day, week-to-week or month-to-month fractional
                      ownership. Automatic payments are scheduled monthly over the life of the agreement up to 99 years.
                    </p>
                  </div>
